## Worker Detail [/worker/{name}/day/{day}]
+ Parameters
    + name (required, string, `Stella`) ... Name of the worker
    + day (required, string, `Monday`) ... Day of the week default: today

    
### List chores for worker by day [GET]

List all chores, for a given worker, for today (default) or any day

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Stella",
            "day": "Monday",
            "chores": [
                "name": "table",
                "name": "playroom right table",
                "name": "Hall and Bath"
            ]
        }